    <item>
      <title>即将离任的美国驻华特使称中美关系正走在“正确道路上”，不要偏离轨道</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/outgoing-us-envoy-to-china-says-ties-on-right-road-don-t-veer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国驻华最高外交官表示，他用 80% 的时间管理与北京的竞争，用 20% 的时间接触北京，并称在华盛顿准备迎接新政府之际，这是正确的平衡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/outgoing-us-envoy-to-china-says-ties-on-right-road-don-t-veer</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 12:00:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>佛罗里达州参议院空缺，拉拉·特朗普的政治奖章即将揭晓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/trump-eyes-loyalist-lara-trump-for-rubio-s-florida-senate-seat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普在为其内阁招募忠诚拥护者的同时，似乎还在考虑在国会山安插另一位忠诚的盟友：他的儿媳拉拉·特朗普。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/trump-eyes-loyalist-lara-trump-for-rubio-s-florida-senate-seat</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芬兰研究恢复地雷以提高防御能力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/finland-to-study-bringing-back-land-mines-to-improve-defenses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芬兰将研究是否重新引入杀伤人员地雷，以加强对北约防御集团与其主要对手之间最长的陆地边界上俄罗斯的防御。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/finland-to-study-bringing-back-land-mines-to-improve-defenses</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 11:46:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙任命中间派贝鲁为法国总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/macron-names-centrist-bayrou-to-be-new-french-prime-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙选择弗朗索瓦·贝鲁担任法国新任总理，呼吁长期的中间派盟友来引导推翻上届政府的分裂政治格局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/macron-names-centrist-bayrou-to-be-new-french-prime-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 11:45:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>财政部信函中隐藏着阻止美国钢铁交易的理由</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/reasons-to-reject-us-steel-deal-are-buried-in-treasury-letter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据称，美国总统乔·拜登计划以国家安全为由，终止新日铁公司以 141 亿美元收购美国钢铁公司的计划。美国财政部 8 月份的一封信提供了这一理由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/reasons-to-reject-us-steel-deal-are-buried-in-treasury-letter</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 18:42:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞击败巴尼耶为下任法国总理提供经验教训</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/how-le-pen-chewed-up-barnier-hold-lessons-for-next-french-pm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即将卸任的法国总理米歇尔·巴尼耶（Michel Barnier）学到了一个惨痛的教训，他的继任者也应该知道这一点。玛丽娜·勒庞（Marine Le Pen）是无法安抚的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/how-le-pen-chewed-up-barnier-hold-lessons-for-next-french-pm</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 17:11:26 GMT</pubDate>
